\tan(\text{angle})=\tan(\text{opposite})/\sin(\text{adjacent})
\tan(60^\circ)/\sin(30^\circ)=\sqrt3/(1/2)=2\sqrt3
\tan(30^\circ)/\sin(60^\circ)=(1/\sqrt3)/(\sqrt3/2)=2/3
\arctan(2\sqrt3)+\arctan(2/3)-90=17.5880^\circ
